THE OBJECT OF THE 'FIND' GAMES IS TOGUIDE THE CURSOR WITH THE JOYSTICKTO A HIDDEN SQUARE ON THE SCREEN.IN 'FIND 1'; THE COLOR OF YOURCURSOR   CHANGES BASED ON HOW CLOSETO THE HIDDENSQUARE YOU ARE.IN 'FIND 2'; THE CURSOR FLASHESFASTER  AS YOU GET CLOSER.IN 'FIND 3'; THERE ARE CLICKINGSOUNDS  THAT GET FASTER AS YOU GETCLOSER.